    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/e2eebf19c1a33f336e2d105616cfeccc.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/e2eebf19c1a33f336e2d105616cfeccc.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/39242e78a3c2d542ae7e10b4d9f8aaaf.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/39242e78a3c2d542ae7e10b4d9f8aaaf.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/39242e78a3c2d542ae7e10b4d9f8aaaf.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Dice Goblin's Den is a 2D side-scrolling Tower Defense Roguelite game where you defend your fellow Goblins from waves of &quot;<i>heroes</i>&quot; who have been given quests at the local tavern to pillage and loot your home! Grow your goblin den and strengthen your economy by journeying to different levels to gather more resources while fending off your enemies! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/a5805aa1dc95d56ba6f510e8bedd3c70.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/a5805aa1dc95d56ba6f510e8bedd3c70.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/01420cc991ee18ca52b73f4886483742.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/01420cc991ee18ca52b73f4886483742.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/01420cc991ee18ca52b73f4886483742.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Unlock new classes to play when you defeat each enemy party leader! Each class has its own abilities that can alter your tactics and benefit your goblins in a unique way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/df80fe938cc4264d25efbc2f0ba33f7b.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/df80fe938cc4264d25efbc2f0ba33f7b.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/c06b867ca771f98092b4cfa3bcccc37f.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=800 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/c06b867ca771f98092b4cfa3bcccc37f.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/c06b867ca771f98092b4cfa3bcccc37f.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Defend yourself from enemy forces who are quested with the task of raiding your party and looting your corpses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/e01a3b05225abdd8349a0fdbccd31c52.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/e01a3b05225abdd8349a0fdbccd31c52.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/7ea506c95f14e1906dcb6c3b8a0a8f9a.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=800 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/7ea506c95f14e1906dcb6c3b8a0a8f9a.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/7ea506c95f14e1906dcb6c3b8a0a8f9a.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Gather resources and manage your own economy, but be wary of the balance of allocating them between combat and worker units. It can be dangerous to spend too many resources hiring workers instead of combat units to defend your goblin den, but sometimes being greedy pays off!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/8d426dfbfbaa888d5daaf559dc02a020.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/8d426dfbfbaa888d5daaf559dc02a020.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/cd7f98a70d1ec3de20b7b2fbf826fc17.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/cd7f98a70d1ec3de20b7b2fbf826fc17.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/cd7f98a70d1ec3de20b7b2fbf826fc17.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Gain resources passively each day by hiring workers and allocating them to gather whichever specific resources you think will best serve your goblin den!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/20eb903e9e0e8355af8166dc927e7e0b.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/20eb903e9e0e8355af8166dc927e7e0b.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/c83b06108c4b5d0933469a642de59b11.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=1170 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/c83b06108c4b5d0933469a642de59b11.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/c83b06108c4b5d0933469a642de59b11.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Upgrade your goblins by way of spells, abilities, and attributes at the cost of resources! But be careful not to put all of your dice in one basket! <i>Goblins together strong!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/14256bb8b6c64261b9b4c6d9fad37fac.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/14256bb8b6c64261b9b4c6d9fad37fac.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/e7271cb7ce69a584d2a0d4aad6904a11.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/e7271cb7ce69a584d2a0d4aad6904a11.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/e7271cb7ce69a584d2a0d4aad6904a11.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">It wouldn't be very dicey without all the uncertainty of a Roguelite, now would it?! Play with randomized levels, enemies, loot, and upgrades! Every playthrough is its own unique experience, and it's up to you to beat the odds by adapting to what luck throws your way, choosing the best rewards for the occasion, and employing clever strategies. But be careful! Defeat will set you right back to the drawing board!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/938e2786140293a4642ab7edd0f55076.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/938e2786140293a4642ab7edd0f55076.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/0251a555833d65b28f2667987f087a9a.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=640 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/0251a555833d65b28f2667987f087a9a.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/0251a555833d65b28f2667987f087a9a.mp4?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Coming soon to a Goblin Den near you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/609009fce137b6f01c852506ffa799e8.apng?t=1771763003\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/609009fce137b6f01c852506ffa799e8.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/31ba5243242e389c87e2b104773972b5.poster.avif?t=1771763003\" width=600 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/31ba5243242e389c87e2b104773972b5.webm?t=1771763003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
